      • BoxConfig

        public BoxConfig(String clientId,
                 String clientSecret,
                 String enterpriseId,
                 String publicKeyID,
                 String privateKey,
                 String privateKeyPassword,
                 EncryptionAlgorithm encryptionAlgorithm)
        Creates a configuration with clientId, clientSecret, publicKeyID, privateKey, privateKeyPassword. and an encryptionAlgorithm.
        Parameters:
        clientId - the client ID of the application
        clientSecret - the client secret of the application
        enterpriseId - the enterprise ID of the box account
        publicKeyID - the unique ID of the uploaded public key
        privateKey - the private key used to sign JWT requests
        privateKeyPassword - the passphrase for the private key
        encryptionAlgorithm - the encryption algorithm that has to be used for signing JWT requests
